data.description: Convenient Living in The Highlands ready for You & Pets! Explore the simplicity of being in the heart of North Tacoma from your new condo. Spacious living room provides a peaceful retreat from your daily routines to stretch out & relax. Updated kitchen features plenty of room to put your chef skills to the test! Large bedrooms are ready to adapt to your changing needs & laundry upstairs is certain to delight. This community boasts plentiful amenities, including a clubhouse, outdoor pools, tennis courts, extra laundry machines & HOA dues include W/S/G! Your central location provides simple access to great schools, WA-16, Pt Defiance, public transit, shopping, dining & so much more! FHA Approved. Schedule your showing today.
